name: Daniel's Broiler - Lake Union
description: Located on the shores of South Lake Union, guests enjoy nightly live music and waterfront dining with stunning views of Lake Union, Gasworks Park and Queen Anne while enjoying USDA Prime Steaks—the top two percent of all graded beef in the nation—as well as other traditional steakhouse favorites and our award-winning wine list.

name: Lakeside South Lake Union
description: For Unforgettable Dining, Just Add Water! Sip and savor the unique epicurean flavors woven masterfully into our ever-changing menu of seasonal & local delights, from our hand-crafted cocktails to our unforgettable seasonally-inspired bites. Culinary Director, Trinity Mack, and her team thoughtfully craft each monthly dinner & brunch menu to create a feast for both the eyes and the palate.
address: 901 Farivew Ave North Suite B110, Seattle, WA 98109-4453

name: Vitality Bowls Seattle
description: Vitality Bowls Seattle opened August 2020 in the city’s South Lake Union area. A metropolitan hub, South Lake Union is home to many major companies, including Amazon, and features an array of restaurants and bars. Customers love stopping by for a delicious acai bowl, smoothie, fresh juice or panini prepared without any ingredient fillers like ice, frozen yogurt, or artificial preservatives.

name: Lassi & Spice
description: Lassi and Spice offers an exciting spin on traditional Indian foods and flavors. The menu centers around our authentic, batch-cooked chai, South Indian-style filter coffee, unique espresso beverages, typical Indian breakfast items (poha, upma, sambar) as well as pastries. Our lassi menu is unique with flavors like mango, pistachio, golden, rose and the traditional salt lassi. We are located in beautiful and booming South Lake Union, and we can't wait to meet you! ​

name: Ba Bar Green
description: Ba Bar Green is a Vegan/East Asian culinary adventure from the folks who brought you Street Food & Cold Drink. While we will certainly appeal to vegans and vegetarians across the board, we also hope to capture the interest of anyone who is curious about plant-based cuisine in general—people who want to eat less meat but aren’t as strict with their diets. Bottom line, this is just good food. The fact that the menu is entirely plant-based is just icing on the gluten-free cake. Join the Banhs and Chef Chris Michel as they explore the flavors or Vietnam, China, Korea, Malaysia, Singapore and more. Entirely vegan. Incredibly delicious. Takeout window open Tuesday through Saturday from 10AM to 6PM. You can enjoy Ba Bar Green at home, the office, or have a seat on our patio in the warmer months. If you are inclined to enjoy an adult beverage, feel free to take your meal inside Ba Bar South Lake Union—we might recommend a Moscow Mule. Cheers!

name: Mbar

name: Flatstick Pub - South Lake Union
description: We're passionate about craft beer and supporting our community. We only offer beer from independent breweries located here in the great state of Washington. You'll never find corporate beer here. We love to have fun, drink beer, and play games. In addition to mini golf you'll find original golf themed games invented by us at Flatstick. Whatever brings you in: first date, delicious beer, team building event, adult birthday party, watching sports, happy hour, or to challenge your friends at a game, our goal is to provide a place where everyone feels welcome to relax and have a great time.

name: Buca di Beppo Italian Restaurant
description: If you are looking for an Italian Restaurant in Seattle, WA then come to Buca. Our Italian Restaurant serves Authentic Family Style Italian Food. Our Seattle location on Westlake Avenue is perfectly situated at the base of Lake Union, afford-ing gorgeous views of the Lake and Lake Union Park to accompany your delicious meals. When the trees are green in the park, you will see how Seattle earned the name "The Emerald City" and when you taste our chef-prepared dishes you will see how we became Seattle's favorite Italian restaurant. We have several catering packages full of everyone's favorites or you can customize a package to your exact needs. Regardless of the event or celebration, your Seattle Buca has got you covered! Make your reservations or come in today!

name: Pardon My Cheesesteak
description: Hungry? Size matters! Get your cheesesteak fix satisfied with a 6″ or 12″ Classic Cheesesteak and a bucket of Loaded Cheesesteak Fries. Get spicy with the Chipotle Cheesesteak. Love Buffalo Chicken? We got Buffalo Chicken Cheesesteak for you! End on a high note with our Brownie Bites. Pardon My Cheesesteak is available for delivery and pick up in select locations nationwide.

name: Caffe Ladro

photo.caption: We bake all our goods in-house to ensure quality and freshness.

description: Now a Seattle coffee institution, Caffe Ladro opened our first location on Upper Queen Anne in 1994. People ask about Caffe Ladro and the company name origin. Caffe Ladro is Italian for coffee thief. When we opened up right next to Starbucks, we intended to pinch their customers with the best staff and coffee we could find. We source and roast all our coffees.
